{
  "stem": "23942.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had a beautiful handwriting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he really-- he knew Hebrew like a sofer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He could write.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I used to see this Gemara.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his presence was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember my father never even removed his watch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He left it on the night table, as if he-- as if he was going get up in the morning, and he is going to pick up the watch, a golden watch.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he left it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't even hidden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was just-- it was just laying on this night table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I knew my father's-- I knew that he's there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- just that we will rejoin him in-- in the near future.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's what I remember of my-- my mother always made us aware of my father-- talked about him, what he was like.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you know and-- and of course, my grandmother, who-- he was the only son, she would always talk about-- I would be always aware that this was her only learned son.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was her granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I was always being made aware that my father wasn't just somewhere-- he was somewhere, but not-- his presence was always near, near.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's what I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our house was very religious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother came from a very religious home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And her father was a Hasid of the Bluzhiver Rebbe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- many dynasties-- in other words, many generations of, of the Bluzhiver dynasty my grandfather followed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was one of his biggest supporters, one of his biggest followers, the closest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was so close that every holiday we'd go-- and I believe in, in some holidays, I don't now if all-- and I know he was a-- the Bluzhiver Rebbe, before he died, I met him.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he remembered what my grandfather said to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
